responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "2A1EFD874B44B255D15E7C96A7A1A3A1", "There\'s plenty of them here! This keep was one of the very first strongholds of the Aelan people. You can tell if you look at the old monuments - that\'s all ancient Aelan! My grandfather said it was already a ruin before our people left for Sanctus all those years ago. These are the oldest ruins in all of the Riverlands! It\'s no wonder the place is haunted!")
